The Chronicle Online Reporter The slain rapper will be buried at a private cemetery on Saturday. <img class="size-large wp-image-680553" src="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2023/02/Untitled-3-5-680x380.jpg" alt="" width="680" height="380" srcset="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2023/02/Untitled-3-5.jpg 680w, https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2023/02/Untitled-3-5-360x200.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" /> The late AKA However, his ex-wife DJ Zinhle will not be accompanied to the burial by her husband Bongani Mohosana, who will miss the ceremony in accordance with cultural protocol. <img class="size-large wp-image-527239" src="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2021/01/DJ-Zinhle-680x380.jpg" alt="" width="680" height="380" srcset="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2021/01/DJ-Zinhle.jpg 680w, https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2021/01/DJ-Zinhle-360x200.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" /> DJ Zinhle AKA’s family released a statement on Tuesday morning with regard to the funeral proceedings, while appreciating the support they received from fans and the Mohosana family. <img class="wp-image-681335 size-large" src="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2023/02/Bongani-680x380.jpg" alt="" width="680" height="380" srcset="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2023/02/Bongani.jpg 680w, https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2023/02/Bongani-360x200.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" /> Bongani Mohosana Reads a statement issued by the Forbes family: “We as the Forbes family would like to acknowledge the outpouring of love we have received over the past few days. Kiernan wasn’t just loved but by the nation, as we’ve seen from loved ones, friends, industry colleagues, media tributes, and the Megacy. It is our wish to celebrate the life of Kiernan with those he touched ad impacted through his gift of music,” read part of the statement. <img class="size-large wp-image-681334" src="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2023/02/aka-680x380.jpg" alt="" width="680" height="380" srcset="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2023/02/aka.jpg 680w, https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2023/02/aka-360x200.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" /> Statement by late AKA’s family on funeral and burial proceedings The family stated that AKA’s memorial service will be open to the public, as well as be streamed online. “Kiernan will be laid to rest in a private provincial funeral on Saturday 18 February 2023. We’d also like to acknowledge our extended family the Mohosanas for their unwavering support during this time, as Bongani Mohosana will be in absentia at the funeral due to observing cultural protocol,” read the statement. AKA’s father Tony Forbes, who has been appointed the official family spokesperson, will give a public statement at 3 pm today.